oring the pore-size\nwithin a definite regime thereby reducing the multimodal trait. The reported\nstudy may be relevant towards applications such as catalysis, sensing and\nfiltration, where pore size distribution plays a crucial role.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Nov 2014 10:09:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-24"}
