ectly\n(e.g., optically) than for molecular fluids which typically call for\nsophisticated X-ray scattering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Nov 2014 15:45:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-24"}
